room_title: Escape room "Flood The City" by Escape House in Overland Park
review: My family and I had a great time. My husband and I took our kids and three of their friends and tried our luck in "Flood the City." It was challenging and exciting. It was fun to work together! Our guide was amazing and very hospitable! We will be coming back soon to try our luck in the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Flood The City" by Escape House in Overland Park
review: First time at an escape room and had a blast! We took on Flood the City. It was a great time and can't wait to go back and try the other rooms. Very friendly staff too.
